text: Kıznaz Türkeli is a Turkish politician of Azerbaijani origin,Hdp'nin İlk Azeri Adayı Mazbatasını Aldı. Haberler.com. 17 June 2015. who won a seat in the Turkish parliament in June 2015 with the Peoples' Democratic Party from electoral district of Iğdır. ==References== Category:Deputies of Iğdır Category:Living people Category:People from Iğdır Category:Turkish people of Azerbaijani descent Category:Members of the 25th Parliament of Turkey Category:Turkish women in politics Category:21st-century women politicians Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
